      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.2",
          "pli": "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. ",
          "en": "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.3",
          "pli": "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā; ",
          "en": "What is ignorance? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.4",
          "pli": "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti? ",
          "en": "And how is an ignorant person defined?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.5",
          "pli": "“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇaṃ—",
          "en": "“Not knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.6",
          "pli": "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā; ",
          "en": "This is called ignorance. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:1.7",
          "pli": "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotīti. ",
          "en": "And this is how an ignorant person is defined. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:2.1",
          "pli": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. ",
          "en": "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.17:2.2",
          "pli": "Sattamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
